OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493903
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FWords by ITV News Correspondent John
OL,6,FRay and Senior Producer Jack Abbey
OL,8,FA sound like thunder seems to rattle
OL,9,Fthe windows of our apartment.
OL,11,FWe jump up and rush to the balcony,
OL,12,Fcameras in hand, thinking it's a
OL,13,Ffighter jet or even the sound of a
OL,14,Fmissile crashing in from Iran.
OL,16,FWe are relieved when we realise it is
OL,17,Fjust the noise of another supercar
OL,18,Frevving through the streets of Dubai
OL,19,FMarina, echoing, deafeningly, off the
OL,20,Fskyscrapers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
