CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493903
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FAlongside cameraman Mark Jervis, we
OL,6,Frepeated that moment many times during
OL,7,Fthe ten days we spent in the United
OL,8,FArab Emirates.
OL,10,FIt neatly sums up the strange
OL,11,Fcontradictions of Dubai over the past
OL,12,Ftwo weeks: one of the richest cities
OL,13,Fin the world under fire whilst trying
OL,14,Fdesperately to continue with life as
OL,15,Fnormal.
OL,17,F''Move along, there's not much to see
OL,18,Fhere,'' might be the official mantra.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
