CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493903
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FDubai's modern wealth was built on its
OL,6,Freputation as a safe haven for
OL,7,Ftourists, trade and expats from around
OL,8,Fthe world.
OL,10,FThe war with Iran - just a short
OL,11,Fmissile or drone journey across the
OL,12,FGulf - has shattered that image.
OL,14,FThe United Arab Emirates has come
OL,15,Funder more frequent attacks than any
OL,16,Fother country targeted by Tehran,
OL,17,Fwhich sees any place hosting US forces
OL,18,Fas a valid target.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493903
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FSeemingly in an effort to protect its
OL,6,Fimage, the Emirates (in which Dubai is
OL,7,Fthe biggest city) has threatened
OL,8,Fsevere consequences, big fines and
OL,9,Feven the prospect of prison for people
OL,10,Ffound to have filmed missile attacks
OL,11,For the resulting damage.
OL,13,FIn the past couple of days a 60 year
OL,14,Fold British man was charged under
OL,15,Ftough cyber-crime laws for allegedly
OL,16,Ffilming missiles over the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493903
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FCombined with the testimony of fear-
OL,6,Ffilled British people returning home
OL,7,Fafter their holidays were abruptly
OL,8,Finterrupted on the February 28, this
OL,9,Fhas created intense speculation on
OL,10,Fsocial media as to what's 'really'
OL,11,Fhappening in Dubai.
OL,13,FIn particular, there are suggestions
OL,14,Fthat the media is failing to give the
OL,15,Ffull picture, that deaths might be
OL,16,Fmuch higher than reported and that
OL,17,FDubai is no longer a safe place to be.
OL,19,FWe were one of a small number of
OL,20,Finternational news teams in the UAE,
OL,21,Farriving the day after the war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FWe found a city on edge, hunkered
OL,6,Fdown, in a position it never expected
OL,7,Fto find itself, uncertain as to how
OL,8,Fthis all ends.
OL,10,FBut we saw nothing that would suggest
OL,11,Fspeculation of large hidden death
OL,12,Ftolls was correct.
OL,14,FOne reason for that is that the UAE's
OL,15,Fair defence system ` in which they
OL,16,Fhave invested heavily - seems to have
OL,17,Fbeen very effective.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FThey claim a ''kill rate'' of well
OL,6,Fover 90% of incoming missiles and
OL,7,Fdrones. Many of them are intercepted
OL,8,Ffar out over the narrow stretch of sea
OL,9,Fwhich separates the UAE from Iran.
OL,11,FThat doesn't mean there's no reason to
OL,12,Fworry in Dubai.
OL,14,FOn our first morning we heard two
OL,15,Flarge explosions not far from our
OL,16,Fhotel on the famous Palm Jumeirah,
OL,17,Fmost likely successful intercepts but
OL,18,Fmuch closer to land.
OL,20,FWhen that happens the biggest risk is
OL,21,Ffrom falling debris.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
