PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FOver the weekend, a skyscraper
OL,6,Fopposite our apartment in the tourist-
OL,7,Fheavy Dubai Marina was hit by falling
OL,8,Fdebris from a late interception, the
OL,9,Fexplosion from which was the loudest
OL,10,Fwe heard.
OL,12,FA taxi driver was killed by falling
OL,13,Ffragments, with his car set ablaze.
OL,15,FAll the images were widely shared and
OL,16,Fmay well have contributed to the
OL,17,Fsocial media crack down.
OL,19,FWe headed out onto the streets to see
OL,20,Fwhat we could find out, wary of the
OL,21,Frules around filming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FAt the base of the tower, a shocked
OL,6,Fand excited - but not panicked - crowd
OL,7,Fof dozens had gathered, some trying to
OL,8,Ffilm, others just watching.
OL,10,FThe day before we arrived, the famous
OL,11,FFairmont Hotel and the Burj Al Arab
OL,12,FHotel had received damage from falling
OL,13,Fdrones and missiles, creating further
OL,14,Ftension amongst the tourists who spoke
OL,15,Fto us.
OL,17,FBut for much of the subsequent week
OL,18,Fand a half we spent in the Gulf, we
OL,19,Fheard very little of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
