OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FRarely were the loud alarms that
OL,6,Fsounded on our mobile phones followed
OL,7,Fby the spectacular night-time light
OL,8,Fshow of air defences in action.
OL,10,FMore often we heard the distant rumble
OL,11,Fof warplanes far overhead.
OL,13,FThe airspace above the UAE and the
OL,14,Fairport in Dubai was closed when the
OL,15,Fwar began (we had to drive in from
OL,16,FSaudi Arabia) and didn't open again
OL,17,Ffor many days.
OL,19,FEven then the openings that did happen
OL,20,Fwere erratic and limited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FThat meant tens of thousands of
OL,6,FBritish tourists were stuck in Dubai
OL,7,Fwith limited means of escape.
OL,9,FWe spent several days reporting their
OL,10,Fstories as they plotted their routes
OL,11,Fout by land and air.
OL,13,FSome were too anxious to speak. Not
OL,14,Fbecause of the war, but rather out of
OL,15,Fa fear of upsetting their hotel
OL,16,Fmanagement, tour operators or the UAE
OL,17,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FWhilst most felt nervous after long
OL,6,Fnights sheltering in hotel basements,
OL,7,Fit felt like more stress was being
OL,8,Fcaused by concerns around financing
OL,9,Fextended stays and the logistics of
OL,10,Ffinding a way back home without access
OL,11,Fto flights from Dubai.
OL,13,FOne young couple from Lancashire,
OL,14,FCaitlyn and Dylan told us: "We're
OL,15,Fgetting to the point where our credit
OL,16,Fcards are maxed out... We're going to
OL,17,Fget the point where everyone is stuck
OL,18,Fwithout any money or any money to get
OL,19,Fhome."
OL,26,@vD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
