CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FSpeaking to tourists is one thing,
OL,6,Fspeaking to resident British expats
OL,7,Fanother.
OL,9,FWhilst the UAE is an outwardly modern,
OL,10,Ftolerant city, when it comes to
OL,11,Fpolitics there's no mistaking: dissent
OL,12,Fis not allowed.
OL,14,FAs journalists that makes it a very
OL,15,Funusual place to operate and much
OL,16,Fharder to build an accurate picture.
OL,18,FAll the while Dubai-based social media
OL,19,Finfluencers praised the government and
OL,20,Fdeclared that they didn't feel afraid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FBut even in the conversations we had
OL,6,Fcasually off-camera, a picture emerged
OL,7,Fof an expat community broadly
OL,8,Fdetermined to see this out.
OL,10,FMore than 200,000 British people have
OL,11,Fmade Dubai their home and faith in the
OL,12,Fgovernment's ability to defend them
OL,13,Fappears strong - despite a war that
OL,14,Fwas in no-one's plans.
OL,16,FOne expat said to us, "The closest
OL,17,Fcomparison I could make to this
OL,18,Fsituation is the Covid lockdowns", as
OL,19,Fhe looked down on the empty streets
OL,20,Fand beaches of a city that was teeming
OL,21,Fjust weeks before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FThe head of the British Chamber of
OL,6,FCommerce in Dubai, Katy Keenan, told
OL,7,Fus business remains resilient.
OL,9,FShe thinks stories of expats leaving
OL,10,Fare overdone.
OL,12,F"The timing of the spring break will
OL,13,Fskew reality as many British families
OL,14,Fhave taken planned holidays and left
OL,15,FDubai with every intention of coming
OL,16,Fback for the new term,'' she reasoned.
OL,18,FTime will tell. The peril for Dubai
OL,19,Fand the rest of the Gulf lies in how
OL,20,Flong the war rages and how far Iran
OL,21,Fgoes in conducting its response.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
