OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,6,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,7,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,8,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,10,FIn recent days there's been some
OL,11,Fevidence of a worrying change in
OL,12,Ftactics.
OL,14,FThe number of missiles and drones
OL,15,Ffired at the UAE has been declining
OL,16,F(perhaps as a result of a degraded
OL,17,FIranian capacity to launch them) but
OL,18,Fthe targets seem to have shifted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FIn the early days of the war, military
OL,6,Fand US-related facilities were the
OL,7,Ffocus of Iranian attacks but on the
OL,8,Fday we flew out of the country two
OL,9,Fdrones crashed close to the airport,
OL,10,Fdelaying flights by hours.
OL,12,FJust on Friday, there were reports of
OL,13,Fdrone attacks in downtown Dubai where
OL,14,Fmost of the city's business and
OL,15,Ffinance is based.
OL,17,FThis shift in focus towards the
OL,18,Fairport, tourist and financial areas
OL,19,Fof the city could prove to greatest
OL,20,Fdanger to Dubai.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773493904
OL,3,CIs Dubai safe? The view from the ground
OL,5,FIf the war continues for many more
OL,6,Fweeks the economic impact could
OL,7,Fquickly become severe.
OL,9,FAs one long term resident said to us:
OL,10,F"Remember there's no oil in this city.
OL,11,FEverything you see if built on trade
OL,12,Fand tourism.
OL,14,F"And if the money doesn't flow, then
OL,15,Fwhat's the point in Dubai?"
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
